<subSubSection pageId="104" pageNumber="704" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="104.[1451,2659,1473,2175]" pageId="104" pageNumber="704">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1453,1801,2024,2058]" pageId="104" pageNumber="704">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Longnosed Mosaic-tailed Rat is widespread and is found in a National Park. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rummler" authorityYear="1935" box="[2519,2658,2064,2098]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Macruromys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="104" pageNumber="704" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="major">No major</taxonomicName>
threats have been reported.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
